{"tid":2285991,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"記者何罪 - 左丁山","createTime":"2020-11-14T14:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T14:47:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31e38bd1257ba8f8b04812e7fd948365f83e43f5","tid":2285991,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201114/I7I62IRN6ZAGBKPEVDF6LH5CVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201114%2FI7I62IRN6ZAGBKPEVDF6LH5CVM%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=86613a98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201114%2FI7I62IRN6ZAGBKPEVDF6LH5CVM%2F&h=865204a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201114/I7I62IRN6ZAGBKPEVDF6LH5CVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n記者何罪 - 左丁山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A51YpmrNAtdbZZb7uHCuywtPsyM=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VV34DZPTMZFHFAEIESK7UFXNXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA51YpmrNAtdbZZb7uHCuywtPsyM%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVV34DZPTMZFHFAEIESK7UFXNXU.jpg&h=0ef11e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n校友Y等更關心新亞新聞系校友蔡玉玲，做調查報導記者做到畀警察拉，以前好似未見過。鏗鏘集係港台節目之寶，公信力極高，能夠擔任鏗鏘集編導，一定係經驗豐富，頭腦慎密之傳媒人，並非心口寫個勇字，橫衝直撞之輩，故此鏗鏘集能在國際上屢屢獲獎，為香港爭光。鏗鏘集編導之中，新亞新聞系校友蕭景路（已故）早年為鏗鏘集立下汗馬功勞，已退休之蔡貞停校友亦表現出色。今有21世紀校友蔡玉玲因「721誰主真相」被拘控，特區政府不准港台為她提供法律支援，不知天理何在，唔通要合約僱員帶律師費返工？"}]}